Metadata-Version: 1.0
Name: django-flashcookie
Version: 0.1.5
Summary: This django application provides rails-like flash messages to Django framework.
Home-page: http://bitbucket.org/offline/django-flashcookie/wiki/Home
Author: Anderson
Author-email: self.anderson@gmail.com
License: BSD
Description: 
        Example:
        ----------
        
        **views.py**
        ::
        
        def some_action(request):
        ...
        request.flash['error'] = "You can't post comments in this section"
        return HttpReponseRedirect("/")
        
        
        **base.html**
        ::
        
        {% if flash %}
        {% for message in flash.error %}
        {{ message }}
        {% endfor %}
        {% endif %}
        
        
        Download:
        ----------
        hg clone http://bitbucket.org/offline/django-flashcookie/
        
        
Keywords: django
Platform: UNKNOWN
